#aalo #aaloparatha #indianfood  #northindia #mashedpotatoes #parathalovers #northindianfood #goodnessofspices #loveforparathas #chutney #peanutchutney #butter #paratha #aaloparatha #paratharecipes #friedpatatoes  #morningbreakfast #kidsfavorite #homecooking  #@journey2.hot_n_healthy.kitchen#

Peanut Chutney
Ingredients
* Roasted peanuts - 1/2 Cup
* Garlic - 2-3
* Green chili - 2
* Cumin seeds - 1/3 Tsp
* Black pepper - 1/3 Tsp
* Salt as per taste
* Water as required

For Tadka
* Oil - 1 Tbsp
*Mustard seeds - 1/2 Tsp
* Dry red chili - 2
* Curry leaves - 6-7
* Asafoetida (hing) - 1 Pinch

Method
* Put roasted peanut in a blender jar, add garlic, green chili, cumin seeds, black pepper, salt, and water.
* Blend into a smooth paste. Transfer in a bowl.
* Heat 1 Tbsp oil in a pan.
*Add mustard seeds, dry red chili, curry leaves and saute for 20sec, add asafoetida and saute for 10 sec.
* Pour the tadka over chutney & mix well.
#stayhealthy #staysafe
